values:
ALright so I am in New York right now...I love it hear! Even though it's been raining since I got in. It's so beautful. I'm not in the City...I'm in the country. It's so awesome. I would love to live in a place like this. The houses are beautiful! There's so much land...it's just awesome. So anyways...Jenn and Troy are probably getting married tomorrow and then I am coming home Friday night. I fly in at 11:38pm. I'm really not looking forward to going back home. It's been really nice not being around my mom so much. I think we will get along much better once I move out. We are just not compatible to be living with each other...which is not uncommon with Mother's and Daugthers. 4 months you guys!!! 4 months and I can MOVE OUT!!!! I can't believe it. It's actually coming really fast. Well, once I got to 8 months away...it was moving really slow. But then when I hit 5 months....time has just flown. The past two months seem like a couple of weeks. It's really nice. I hope it continues like this!!! lol...alright well anyways. I will try to get to the mall and get everyone a present. I can't make any promises though. We don't have a car 98% of the time. But I will try!!! I love you all! I will see you when I get home!!!!!!

XoXo,
Julie

Rules:

  • Don't be rude in my journal to me, or my friends...but especially my friends. You hurt them, I hurt you!! Yes, this does include..the voices! 
  • You should preferably update your journal at least every now and then!! I take interest in other people's truely blunt emotions!
  • Take a note that my journal is NOT about being fake...it's about the real feelings inside! That I really feel!! That are really real feelings!! I do not fake my real feelings. That would make them...fake...really fake feelings! Thus making everything I stand for....FAKE!! And that....makes me....hurt inside!! Thus again...bringing terribly real feelings...that I will have to write about!! So as you can tell...I would be caught in a terribly real bubble filled with problems and terribly real emotions! *dramatic sigh* *hand to forehead*
  • WARNING:  Don't like my really real feelings?? Don't read it!!
  • ALSO WARNING: I am a bit strange...if you couldn't tell from that which is stated in the  above statement!! Prepare yourself!
  • ALSO WARNING AGAIN:  Look at picture above! Ring a bell?? That's right...drama masks...I have a theatrical persona that often times overflows with bubbly emotions... like an over boiled pot of passion..and..feelings! Real feelings...that I really feel...that are really real feelings!!
